                "field_identifier": "ENR",
                "value": 0.96
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Six 96Mo targets with an isotopic",
                "enrichment of (96+-0.1) % were prepared as self-",
                "supporting foils with a thickness of about 1 mg/cm2",
                "Isotopic contaminants of 95Mo, 97Mo, and 98Mo with each",
                "and 98Mo with each about 1% abundance."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Each target was irradiated for 5?20 hours.",
                "The waiting time between the end of bombardment and",
                "start of counting was between 50 and 100 minutes"
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "GSPEC"
